Patricia Ja Lee https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patricia_Ja_Lee 0 Patricia Ja Lee (born July 19, 1975) is an American actress and model. She is best known for her roles of Cassie Chan, the Pink Ranger on the television series Power Rangers Turbo and Power Rangers in Space and as the voice and motion capture actress for Jill Valentine in numerous entries in the Resident Evil franchise of video games.
